<sect1 id="xfce-utils-intro">
  <title>Introduction</title>

  <para>The &app; package provides a taskbar a run dialog and several very
    useful scripts that are also used by other XFce 4 components such as the 
    panel and the desktop mouse menu.
  </para>

</sect1>

